Summary: This document provides an overview of the NavigationRegion2D class in Godot Engine, detailing its purpose and related tutorials.

NavigationRegion2D is a node that defines a navigation area in 2D space. It is used to bake navigation meshes for pathfinding.

Tutorials:
* Using NavigationRegions
